:'''Man With Luscious Hair:''' Hum! Nothing special, so boring here...
:'''Man With Luscious Hair:''' Everyone is wearing the same clothes. This is an obliteration of the staff's individuality!
:<!--Custom String Trigger: Wait_Option_2000206_37-->
:<!--Custom String Listener: Wait_Option_2000206_37-->
:{{DIcon|Arrow}} This hairstyle is so cool!
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_200020604-->
::'''Man With Luscious Hair:''' Mm... not bad, you've got nice taste. The space station has a strict dress code for all researchers. I have to express myself with the smaller details.
::'''Man With Luscious Hair:''' Highlights? Too obscure. Bob cut? Too unsightly. Bald? Too hard to pull off. Now this hairstyle is just right. It's big, curly and puffy. It feels so good when I swing my head.
:{{DIcon|Arrow}} Well... Didn't expect to be running into the fashion police today...
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_200020607-->
::'''Man With Luscious Hair:''' Fashion police? It's true, I do have quite the authority on fashion! So... Thanks!
::'''Man With Luscious Hair:''' Your silver hair is not bad either. It seems you and I have similar tastes in hairstyle.
::'''Man With Luscious Hair:''' The last person I connected with was a "screenwriter" on my home planet &mdash; we call them screenwriters. In the cosmos, you call them storytellers.
:{{DIcon|Arrow}} Where did you get your hair done?
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_200020611-->
::'''Man With Luscious Hair:''' As long as you are determined, anything is possible, anywhere! All you have to do is pick up some Dark Matches from the storage zone &mdash; Oh, although I heard all these things have been stolen by the Antimatter Legion &mdash; anyway, then you light up a bit of Lightless Phosphorous Powder on the experiment bench...
::'''Man With Luscious Hair:''' Recite to yourself, "Babracadabra, make my wish plethora," then...
::'''Man With Luscious Hair:''' Boom! There you have it! Your very own luscious hairstyle.
:<!--Custom String Trigger: TalkSentence_200020614-->
:<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_200020614-->
:'''Man With Luscious Hair:''' Okay, okay. Normally I am not supposed to talk to people outside of the Invincible Space Warhead Association. But after all, this is our {{Color|keyword|nobold=1|first}} conversation...
:'''Man With Luscious Hair:''' In the future, if we can't get what the other is talking about, then let's not waste each other's time.
:<!--Custom String Trigger: ALL_TALK_END-->
:<!--Custom String Listener: ALL_TALK_END-->
:<!--Ends the current performance-->
:<!--Custom String Trigger: Mission_200031201-->
