:'''Man With Luscious Hair:''' Hush... So you did come back for a {{Color|keyword|nobold=1|second}} conversation with me. Are you interested in learning about the Invincible Space Warhead Association?
:<!--Custom String Trigger: Wait_Option_2000207_58-->
:<!--Custom String Listener: Wait_Option_2000207_58-->
:{{DIcon|Arrow}} That sounds awesome!
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_200020703-->
::'''Man With Luscious Hair:''' Yeah, you are on the right track!
:{{DIcon|Arrow}} It's just the Curlcademy, right?
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_200020705-->
::'''Man With Luscious Hair:''' Hey! What do you know!? It's important for an organization to have a cool name.
::'''Man With Luscious Hair:''' According to your theory, the "Stellaron" everyone is scrambling for is just a &mdash; oh, forget it. I can't tell you this.
:<!--Custom String Trigger: TalkSentence_200020707-->
:<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_200020707-->
:'''Man With Luscious Hair:''' Right now, although the Invincible Space Warhead Association is still in its initial stage, we are having great momentum when it comes to expanding our numbers.
:'''Man With Luscious Hair:''' Before long, we will have big, curly, puffy members in every hidden corner of the space station.
:'''Man With Luscious Hair:''' Not to mention, we have secured investment capital from the Interastral Peace Corporation to study the correlation between Lightless Phosphorous Powder and hair volume.
:'''Man With Luscious Hair:''' Now is a good chance to join us! When we develop into the Invincible Space Warhead Corporation, there will be no room for outsiders.
:'''Man With Luscious Hair:''' The way to join us is also very simple. First become big, curly and puffy, then you can sign up with me.
:<!--Custom String Trigger: ALL_TALK_END-->
:<!--Custom String Listener: ALL_TALK_END-->
:<!--Ends the current performance-->
