:'''Man With Luscious Hair:''' With such a great feeling, are you still not impressed after having dealt with me {{Color|keyword|nobold=1|three}} times?
:<!--Custom String Trigger: Wait_Option_2000208_76-->
:<!--Custom String Listener: Wait_Option_2000208_76-->
