::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_200020803-->
::'''Man With Luscious Hair:''' My experiment station got blown up after I recited "Babracadabra, make my wish plethora."
::'''Man With Luscious Hair:''' My research is suspended until the Security Department arranges a new station for me.
:{{DIcon|Arrow}} Which department are you from?
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_200020806-->
::'''Man With Luscious Hair:''' Don't know, don't care. One day, there will be a Herta Department of Curlcademy in the space station, where all the hairstyle aficionados can gather and share knowledge about the art of hairstyling.
::'''Man With Luscious Hair:''' I have already figured out the title of the paper we will publish in collaboration: "On the positive functional relationship between the concentration of scientists with luscious hairstyles and the prosperity and great discoveries of the universe."
